    "To put it another way, can we assume that there exists a way to integrate the two components of such a hypothetical hybrid T3/GPT-LLM's bottom-up T3-grounded internal vocabulary component and its ungrounded top-down GPT/LLM component's \"internal\" vocabulary, as if it were something like an internal verbal dialogue between a grounded T3 teacher and a grounded T3 learner?",
